    dc:description "FIGURES 40–48. Adult males of Propsilocerus paradoxus (Lundstrṏm). 40, part of hypopygium in dorsal view; 41, part of hypopygium in ventral view; 42, 45, median volsella; 43, transverse sternapodeme, phallapodeme and aedeagal lobe; 44, gonostylus; 46–47, tergite IX; 48, anal point. Scale bar is 50 μm." ;
